    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239018>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 12. Habitus. 7. HT ♂ P. trimaculatus Lea, 1918 sp. res., 38.0 mm (photo: Photo: Laura Fazzalari, The Museum Board of South Australia 2011); 8. PT ♂ P. detzneri Kriesche, 1923 nov. syn., 38.0 mm (photo: U. Nylander); 9. PT ♂ P. detzneri Kriesche, 1923 nov. syn., lateral view (photo: U. Nylander); 10. HT ♀ P. lima Pascoe, 1866, 48.8 mm (photo: M. Barklay, BMNH); 11. ♀ P. lima Pascoe, 1866, 47.0 mm (photo: photo: M. Eulàlia Gass i Miracle, RMNH); 12. ♀ P. lima, lateral view (photo: photo: M. Eulàlia Gass i Miracle, RMNH)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239018/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239019>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 18. Habitus. 13. HT ♂ P. gigas Aurivillius, 1926, 41.0 mm (photo: photo: M. Eulàlia Gass i Miracle, RMNH); 14. HT ♀ P. rosenbergii Vollenhoven, 1871, 44.0 mm (photo: M. Eulàlia Gass i Miracle, RMNH); 15. HT ♂ P. rosenbergii ferrugineus Kriesche, 1923, 32.5 mm (photo: Stephan Gottwald, MNHUB); 16. ♂ P. rosenbergii, 38.0 mm (photo: L. Bezark); 17. HT ♀ P. rosenbergii Vollenhoven, 1871, lateral view (photo: M. Eulàlia Gass i Miracle, RMNH); 18. HT ♀ P. wolfi Berchmans, 1925 sp. res., 46.0 mm (photo: M. Eulàlia Gass i Miracle, ZMA)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239019/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239031>
    dc:description "FIGURE 81. Known records of Potemnemus spp. (red numbers) and Periaptodes spp. (blue numbers) from Australia, the island of New Guinea, Moluccas and Solomon Islands. 1. Potemnemus ennevei De Jong, 1947, 2. Potemnemus kaszabi (Breuning, 1973), 3. Potemnemus lima Pascoe, 1866, 4. Potemnemus nylanderi Wallin & Kvamme, 2014 nov. sp., 5. Potemnemus pristis Pascoe, 1866, 6. Potemnemus rosenbergii Vollenhoven van, 1871, 7. Potemnemus scabrosus (Olivier, 1790), 8. Potemnemus sepicanus Kriesche, 1923, 9. Potemnemus thomsoni Lansberge, 1880 sp. res., 10. Potemnemus trimaculatus Lea, 1918 sp. res., 11. Potemnemus tuberifer Gahan, 1894, 12. Potemnemus wheatcrofti (Breuning, 1971) comb. nov., 13. Potemnemus wolfi Berchmans, 1925 sp. res., 14. Periaptodes frater (Van de Poll, 1887), 15. Periaptodes lictor Pascoe, 1866, 16. Periaptodes olivieri (Thomson, 1864), 17. Periaptodes potemnemoides Kriesche, 1936, 18. Periaptodes testator Pascoe, 1866, 19. Periaptodes paratestator Breuning, 1980." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239031/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

